d backscattering-free\nresonances, needed for various applications such as frequency combs, solitons,\nsensing, and other nonlinear optical processes such as photon blockade, and\nregenerative oscillators.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sun, 7 May 2023 17:35:33 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-05-09"}
